INPUT_FILE                  sample.txt
BIN_SCALING_FACTOR          1
VALUE_SCALING_FACTOR        1
FILE_TYPE_HANDLER           SRIM_EXYZ     
OUTPUT_FILE                 sample.mca

This is a parameter file for the txt2mca code.
Possible parameters can be inferred from the code in 
read_config.c.  At some point I may write better 
documentation for this.
If you change the format of the file, prepare for unforseen
consequences.
